    "body": "> What's the use-case? \r\n\r\nIn a system that relies heavily on process liveness, such as Kubernetes, this feature would enhance the ease of restarting and enable the entire pod to reload any necessary data.\r\n\r\n> You're deploying a new VC and you forgot to add keys?\r\n\r\nWhen deploying a new VC without adding keys, this could be a temporary issue associated with acquiring the appropriate keys and generating the configuration. If the LH were to pull the configuration from a remote URL instead of a static config file, it could also alleviate some situations.",
